    public interface Basic2DAgent
extends SpatialAgent<Basic2DAgent,BasicContext<Basic2DEnvironment,Basic2DAgent>,org.asoem.greyfish.utils.space.Point2D,Basic2DAgentContext>
    A basic configuration of a spatial agent with an Point2D projection into space to get simulated in an Basic2DEnvironment.
